summary: TL*THE CONTACT OWNS A 2005 (NA) GLENDALE TITANIUM 34E39SD FIFTH WHEEL TRAILER.  THE TRAILER IS UNABLE TO CORRECTLY ATTACH OR LATCH ITSELF TO THE VEHICLE, WHICH CAUSES INSTABILITY.  THROUGH RESEARCH, THE CONTACT DISCOVERED NUMEROUS COMPLAINTS FOR THE SAME FAILURE.  THE VIN AND FAILURE MILEAGE WERE NOT APPLICABLE.
